notes.body:
Description
This is a metabolism model of Lactococcus lactis subsp. cremoris MG1363 in SBML format.
The content of this model has been carefully created in a manual research effort. This file has been exported from the software COBRApy and further processed with the JSBML-based ModelPolisher application.
This file has been produced by the Systems Biology Research Group using BiGG Models knowledge-base version of Aug 1, 2017, where it is currently hosted and identified by: iNF517.
